metadata.name: Freaky Monkey
metadata.description:
1 of 6 

Dedicated to my Friend Diamond. she passed away 2018. 
the NFT is of a funny rare moments when i caught her doing weird freaky stuff. I got this monkey while on expeditions in the Forest and diamond mining areas in Sierra Leone in 2016 in the Kenema region while heading to Kono. I got her from Hunters and kept her for about 2 years b4 she got killed by stray Dogs, one night while i was sleeping.....
